task.summary: - More refactoring - The SensorActivity now has a spinner with all of the detected sensors - I have finally added the YanuX Scavenger application icon, replacing the generic Android logo.
- The sensor spinner is now fully working and the selected sensor name is displayed. I still have to display other properties and the values from the sensor. - More refactoring.
- The Sensors Activity is mostly finished (at least as far as a minimally functional version goes) - More refactoring.
- Wear App now supports Round and Square screens with the same shared layout - More refactoring.
- Wear App now supports Round and Square screens with the same shared layout - More refactoring.
- Streamlining of the Wi-Fi scanning code is in progress - Permission management has been generalized - More refactoring.
- Removed some unused code - More refactoring.
- APKs generated for easier distribution - Some clean up here and there - Removed some unused code - More refactoring

MESSAGE.value: - Some refactoring - Started to work on dedicated Activities to Scavenge separate types of data ;)
- More refactoring - The SensorActivity now has a spinner with all of the detected sensors - I have finally added the YanuX Scavenger application icon, replacing the generic Android logo.
- The sensor spinner is now fully working and the selected sensor name is displayed. I still have to display other properties and the values from the sensor. - More refactoring.
- The Sensors Activity is mostly finished (at least as far as a minimally functional version goes) - More refactoring.
- Wear App now supports Round and Square screens with the same shared layout - More refactoring.
- Streamlining of the Wi-Fi scanning code is in progress - Permission management has been generalized - More refactoring.
- Removed some unused code - More refactoring.
- APKs generated for easier distribution - Some clean up here and there - Removed some unused code - More refactoring
